<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM4.5">
<l>māṭa māḷikai cūḻmatu raippati</l>
<l>nāṭi nanteru viṉnaṭu vēvantiṭ</l>
<l>ṭōṭai māmata yāṉai yutaittavaṉ</l>
<l>kūṭu mākilnī kūṭiṭu kūṭalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O circle! [You] be joined if</l>
<l rend="indent">He who kicked the big, rutting elephant with a forehead plate,</l>
<l rend="indent">comes seeking [us] in the middle of our street seeking [us]</l>
<l rend="indent">in the city of Mathurā surrounded by palaces with storeys,</l>
<l>and unites with [me].</l>
     </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
